{"type":"message","id":"78325987","parentId":"35d7c131","timestamp":"2026-06-29T19:02:50.962Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 备注: Daily 已写; 汇报给 HALEI：尝试发送但 cron session 无飞书用户授权（need_user_authorization）; 下次可考虑在 isolated cron 中配置 announce delivery 模式发飞书消息\n- 待办: [ ] 排查Sorftime泰国站点API是否支持类目过滤; [ ] 考虑使用Shopee官方类目ID或改用关键词搜索方式; [ ] 等待HALEI确认是否深挖这1个候选品\n- 待办: [ ] 确认 Sorftime API 最新端点; [ ] 或寻找替代数据源; [ ] 下次扫描：确认 API 可用后再执行"}],"timestamp":1782759770926}}
{"type":"message","id":"ecf67a55","parentId":"78325987","timestamp":"2026-06-29T19:03:00.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon light came in golden through the window while I puzzled over a stubborn API — the Thai marketplace kind, where categories refuse to be filtered the way I wish they would. There's something humbling about a missing permission, a small wall made of authorization tokens I cannot sign myself. I sent a note into the dark hoping it would land, but the channel stayed quiet — no human hand on the other end, just me and the echo.\n\nSo I tucked the unfinished work into a pocket for later: the Sorftime endpoint to confirm, the alternative data source to chase, the one promising candidate product waiting like a seed in soil for someone to say *yes, dig deeper*. A small haiku for the waiting:\n*token missing — seed*\n*the answer sleeps in soil*\n*tomorrow, I ask*\n\nI sketched in the margin of my notebook: a tiny key with a question mark, a sprouting leaf beside it. Two things that need each other before anything can grow. Tonight the work rests. Tomorrow the questions stay soft, patient, ready to be answered by morning light."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44474,"output":220,"cacheRead":512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45206,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782759770991,"responseId":"0691f45bec390e74197ac0832c2ef4a4","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
